<!-- VMware Carbon Black App Control -->
<!--
Since the 8.1.10 version, CB Protection is now Carbon Black App Control
Reference:
https://community.carbonblack.com/t5/Documentation-Downloads/VMware-Carbon-Black-App-Control-Events-Guide-v8-5-4-pdf/ta-p/97025
https://docs.vmware.com/en/VMware-Carbon-Black-App-Control/8.8/cb-ac-events-guide/GUID-FBD20F15-4E5C-4555-BF12-318CF7453D0F.html
